---
// src/components/Approach.astro
---

<section class="approach" aria-labelledby="approach-title">
  <div class="approach-container">
    <div class="approach-intro">
      <div class="approach-heading-group">
        <p class="approach-eyebrow">Our approach</p>

        <h2 id="approach-title" class="approach-title">
          AI succeeds when the operating system around it works.
        </h2>
      </div>

      <div class="approach-copy">
        <p>
          Technology is rarely the only constraint. The harder work is aligning
          customer needs, business priorities, data, workflows, governance, and
          frontline behavior.
        </p>

        <p>
          Cadence Lab does not treat AI as a standalone implementation. We
          design the conditions that make it useful, trusted, measurable, and
          sustainable in real customer-facing environments.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="approach-grid">
      <article class="approach-item">
        <span class="approach-number" aria-hidden="true">01</span>

        <h3>Diagnose the operating environment</h3>

        <p>
          We examine customer friction, team ownership, decision paths, legacy
          systems, CRM data, and the constraints shaping current performance.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="approach-item">
        <span class="approach-number" aria-hidden="true">02</span>

        <h3>Translate strategy into workflows</h3>

        <p>
          We turn executive priorities and stakeholder requirements into clear,
          repeatable processes that teams can understand and use.
        </p>
      </article>

      <article class="approach-item">
        <span class="approach-number" aria-hidden="true">03</span>

        <h3>Connect adoption to measurable outcomes</h3>

        <p>
          We define the behaviors, governance, data signals, and performance
          measures needed to improve customer and business results over time.
        </p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .approach {
    width: 100%;
    padding-block: clamp(4rem, 9vw, 7rem);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    background: var(--color-surface);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .approach-container {
    display: flex;
    width: min(calc(100% - (2 * var(--page-gutter))), var(--container-page));
    margin-inline: auto;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: clamp(3rem, 7vw, 5rem);
  }

  .approach-intro {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 0.9fr) minmax(0, 1.1fr);
    gap: clamp(2rem, 6vw, 5rem);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .approach-heading-group {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .approach-eyebrow {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-blue);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.4;
    letter-spacing: 0;
    text-transform: none;
  }

  .approach-title {
    max-width: 16ch;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: clamp(2rem, 1.55rem + 1.8vw, 3.5rem);
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.04;
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .approach-copy {
    display: grid;
    max-width: 42rem;
    gap: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: clamp(1.0625rem, 1rem + 0.25vw, 1.25rem);
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.65;
  }

  .approach-copy p {
    margin: 0;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  .approach-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .approach-item {
    display: flex;
    min-width: 0;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 1rem;
    padding: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2.75rem);
  }

  .approach-item + .approach-item {
    border-left: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .approach-number {
    color: var(--color-blue);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.4;
  }

  .approach-item h3 {
    max-width: 24ch;
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: clamp(1.125rem, 1.05rem + 0.3vw, 1.375rem);
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 600;
    line-height: 1.25;
    letter-spacing: -0.015em;
    text-wrap: balance;
  }

  .approach-item p {
    margin: 0;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    font-family: var(--font-sans);
    font-size: 0.9375rem;
    font-style: normal;
    font-weight: 400;
    line-height: 1.6;
    text-wrap: pretty;
  }

  @media (max-width: 56rem) {
    .approach-intro {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      gap: 1.75rem;
    }

    .approach-title {
      max-width: 18ch;
    }

    .approach-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .approach-item + .approach-item {
      border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
      border-left: 0;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 40rem) {
    .approach {
      padding-block: clamp(3.5rem, 14vw, 5rem);
    }

    .approach-title {
      max-width: 15ch;
      font-size: clamp(2rem, 8vw, 2.75rem);
    }

    .approach-copy {
      font-size: 1.0625rem;
    }

    .approach-item {
      padding: 1.5rem 0;
    }
  }

  @media (forced-colors: active) {
    .approach-grid,
    .approach-item {
      border-color: CanvasText;
    }
  }
</style>
